<script language="javascript" src="../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js"></script><script language="javascript" src="../../_dwr/engine.js"></script><script language="javascript" src="/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js"></script><script language="javascript" src="/system/resource/js/ajax.js"></script><form name="_newscontent_fromname">


            <h1 class="article-title text-center">紧急购置设备公告（二次）</h1>
            <div class="article-sm text-center">时间：2026-07-10<span>点击：<script>_showDynClicks("wbnews", 2115661692, 11590)</script>次</span></div>
            <div class="article-p">
             <div id="vsb_content"><div class="v_news_content">
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">一、项目名称：</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">紧急购置设备一批。气垫床</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">张、氧气流量表</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、简易呼吸器</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、水银血压计</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、瞳孔笔</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、开口器</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、舌钳</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、压舌板</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、轮椅</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、治疗盘</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">26</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、弯盘</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个、消毒瓶架</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个，病历夹</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">149</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个，共计</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">15</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">类零星设备。</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">预算</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">总</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">价：</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.2456</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">万</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">元</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">二、报名条件：</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">具有营业执照、税务登记证、组织代码证（或三证合一的营业执照）、银行开户许可证或基本账户存款信息（加盖银行公章）、税收缴纳证明、社会保障资金缴纳证明（提供最新日期不少于一个季度纸质版证明）</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">,</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;"> <span style="font-family: 宋体;">投标企业法定代表人授权书及被授权人身份证（法定代表人投标仅提供法定代表人身份证）</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">报名地点：西安市第五医院设备科</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">联系人：</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">李</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">老师</span> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 宋体;">联系电话：</span><span style="font-family: Calibri;">029-84696321</span></span></p>
